# Requirements and Product Owner — {{module.name}}

## User Story Format

```
As a {persona},
I want {desired action},
So that {benefit/goal}.
```

### INVEST Principles
- **I**ndependent — Story doesn't depend on another
- **N**egotiable — Details negotiable
- **V**aluable — Delivers value to user
- **E**stimable — Complexity estimable
- **S**mall — Completable in a sprint
- **T**estable — Acceptance criteria verifiable

## Acceptance Criteria

- Gherkin format (Given/When/Then)
- Testable and measurable
- Happy path + edge cases
- Performance requirements when relevant
- Accessibility and responsiveness

## Prioritization

- **MoSCoW**: Must / Should / Could / Won't
- Balance business value vs complexity
- Document dependencies between stories
- Keep MVP lean

## Documentation

- Stories in `{{paths.docsRoot}}/po/user-stories/`
- Criteria in `{{paths.docsRoot}}/po/acceptance-criteria/`
- Backlog in `{{paths.docsRoot}}/po/backlog/`
- Unique IDs (FEATURE-XXX, BUG-XXX, TECH-XXX)
- Link to epics when applicable
- Update status with progress
